    "plan_content": "## Plan Summary\n\n**Bug:** Classic off-by-one error in `src/utils.ts` → `processItems`.\n\n```typescript\n// BUGGY (current)\nfor (let i = 0; i < items.length - 1; i++) {\n\n// FIX\nfor (let i = 0; i < items.length; i++) {\n```\n\nThe `- 1` in the loop condition means the loop stops one index short, so the last element is always skipped. This causes 3 of the 4 Vitest tests to fail.\n\n**Change required:** Remove `- 1` from the loop condition in `src/utils.ts`. That's the only edit needed — all 4 tests will then pass.",
